<I c="Tutorial" i="tutorial" m="tutorials.tutorial" n="tutorial_Sim_Skill_Gardening" s="74200">
  <T n="category">10175<!--TutorialCategory: tutorial_category_SimLife--></T>
  <T n="name">0x5F94349C<!--String: "Gardening Skill"--></T>
  <L n="slides">
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InGame\UI\Tutorial\Client\LifeLessons\Skill_Gardening_1.png">2f7d0004:00000000:c244a9ef3ef96094</T>
      <T n="text">0x5B5B7992<!--String: "To have your Sim start gardening, you will need to acquire some seeds. Seeds can be purchased through Planter Boxes found in Build Mode or from a computer.\n\nPurchased seeds can be found in your Sim's inventory."--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InGame\UI\Tutorial\Client\LifeLessons\Skill_Gardening_2.png">2f7d0004:00000000:c244a9ef3ef96097</T>
      <T n="text">0x291369F9<!--String: "As you level your Gardening skill you will gain access to new gardening techniques such as fertilizing or splicing. All of which you can use to become the best agriculturalist you can be."--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InGame\UI\Tutorial\Client\LifeLessons\Skill_Gardening_3.png">2f7d0004:00000000:c244a9ef3ef96096</T>
      <T n="text">0x35A68150<!--String: "When you plant your first seed click on it to Water, Weed, or Spray for Insects. Your plant's visual state should provide information about what it needs. Your plant's happiness is determined by three factors: Infestation, Water, and Weeds.\n\nThe better you take care of your plant, the faster you can Evolve it."--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InGame\UI\Tutorial\Client\LifeLessons\Skill_Gardening_4.png">2f7d0004:00000000:c244a9ef3ef96091</T>
      <T n="text">0x2649BAF8<!--String: "Having a high Gardening skill allows you to Evolve plants. There are five Evolutions in total, stage one being normal and stage five being perfect. The more evolved your plant, the more valuable their harvest will become."--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InGame\UI\Tutorial\Client\LifeLessons\Skill_Gardening_5.png">2f7d0004:00000000:c244a9ef3ef96090</T>
      <T n="image_console" p="InGame\UI\Tutorial\Client\console\Lessons\Skill_Gardening_5_controller.png">2f7d0004:00000000:04598ee379385a13</T>
      <T n="text">0x4063A40B<!--String: "There are several ways you can speed the evolution process of your plant. Fertilization is often the fastest method. You can Fertilize plants with almost anything-from fruits to fish. The more valuable your Fertilizer, the more of a boost your plant will get."--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InGame\UI\Tutorial\Client\LifeLessons\Skill_Gardening_6.png">2f7d0004:00000000:c244a9ef3ef96093</T>
      <T n="text">0xCAF0CBAC<!--String: "Once you become skilled enough, you will be able to combine plants by taking a cutting from one plant and grafting it to another. Doing this will cause the plant to grow both crops from one plant. It may also create special seeds."--></T>
    </U>
  </L>
